''[[Moff Weblin]]'' was a [[fleet tender]] in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] named after [[Grand Moff/Legends|Grand Moff]] [[Weblin]]. At some point during the years of the [[New Order/Legends|New Order]], it was assigned to [[Sixth Negative Regions|Black Sword Command]], with [[Davith Sconn]] serving as the bridge officer in charge of the second watch. About three years after the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] established the [[Black Fifteen]] shipyard at [[N'zoth]], the ''Weblin'' put in for repairs to a damaged number four [[Power cell/Legends|power cell]]. It was in drydock when the Yevetha rose up against the Empire and took control of the facility.

